summary: Both REQ-1 and REQ-2 are fully implemented. The static sitemap.xml is present at frontend/public/sitemap.xml with all required pages (Home, Destinations, Packages, Plan Trip, Community, Contact, and individual destination detail pages), each with <loc>, <lastmod>, <changefreq>, and <priority> elements using the canonical domain https://safarx.in. The index.html has the <link rel="sitemap"> tag, and robots.txt is present with the correct Sitemap directive and wildcard Allow rule. No hallucinated features were detected.
